features: The GPS service of this GPS tracker covers the entire United States and the world, with a wide range. The GPS tracker comes with an embedded built-in SIM card to use Google Maps worldwide and receive GPS tracker location alerts via IOS/Android app.

【Tiny and Slim Design】The size of GPS tracker for vehicles is only 2.20x2.20x0.74 in, its weight is only 1.72 oz. So tiny and equipment with strong magnetic, it can easily be hidden or be adsorbed anywhere. Strong magnetic of GPS tracker is very convenient to use in our lives and is suitable for a variety of tracking paths

【Operate Conveniently&Real-time Control】Turn it on and then automatic connect after sign in app. Friendly interface, you can easily get location, track maps, set geofence and alarms. You can use GPS tracker to locate children, pets, wallets, keys, luggage, etc., and can also be used to remind the alarm clock and other functions.

【Battery Life】Rechargeable battery life of GPS strong magnetic vehicle anti-lost tracker is up to 5 days (the more it moves the lesser the days) .You can set tracking real time every 1-5 minutes. If real time tracking is not needed, battery lasts 30-75 days tracking 1-3 times per day (using battery save mode). Long time to use allows you to travel more at ease.
【Friendly Subscription Fee】Only 18.99$ for each month. Lowest up to 12.4$ per month if you subscribe one year.

【Warranty】we offer 13-month warranty and 7*24 customer service. If you encounter any question about this tracker, please contact us at any time. If you encounter any problems in the use of GPS tracker for vehicles, please feel free to communicate with me. We will provide you with the best service, please feel free to use!
